{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775879438247,"sessionID":"ses_2855a9203ffebYGUS0ExwEQGNY","part":{"id":"prt_d7aa96a5b001Tc13iybFhK9pkF","messageID":"msg_d7aa8f5d20017JmfCInSCqfNMf","sessionID":"ses_2855a9203ffebYGUS0ExwEQGNY","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_b2d837c0cde8469eb2056451","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"suite: AgentCube Router Tests\ntemplates:\n  - agentcube-router.yaml\ntests:\n  - it: should render agentcube-router deployment with default values\n    asserts:\n      - isKind:\n          of: Deployment\n        documentIndex: 0\n      - equal:\n          path: metadata.name\n          value: agentcube-router\n      - equal:\n          path: spec.replicas\n          value: 1\n      - equal:\n          path: spec.template.spec.containers[0].name\n          value: agentcube-router\n      - equal:\n          path: spec.template.spec.containers[0].image\n          value: ghcr.io/volcano-sh/agentcube-router:latest\n      - equal:\n          path: spec.template.spec.containers[0].imagePullPolicy\n          value: IfNotPresent\n      - isNull:\n          path: spec.template.spec.serviceAccountName\n      - contains:\n          path: spec.template.spec.containers[0].args\n          content: --port=8080\n      - contains:\n          path: spec.template.spec.containers[0].args\n          content: --debug\n\n  - it: should render agentcube-router service with default values\n    asserts:\n      - isKind:\n          of: Service\n        documentIndex: 1\n      - equal:\n          path: metadata.name\n          value: agentcube-router\n      - equal:\n          path: spec.type\n          value: ClusterIP\n      - equal:\n          path: spec.ports[0].port\n          value: 8080\n      - equal:\n          path: spec.ports[0].targetPort\n          value: 8080\n      - equal:\n          path: spec.selector.app\n          value: agentcube-router\n\n  - it: should set WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL with release namespace\n    release:\n      namespace: my-namespace\n    asserts:\n      - contains:\n          path: spec.template.spec.containers[0].env\n          content:\n            name: WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL\n            value: http://workloadmanager.my-namespace.svc.cluster.local:8080\n\n  - it: should render with custom service account name\n    set:\n      router:\n        serviceAccountName: custom-router-sa\n    asserts:\n      - equal:\n          path: spec.template.spec.serviceAccountName\n          value: custom-router-sa\n\n  - it: should render with custom replicas and image\n    set:\n      router:\n        replicas: 3\n        image:\n          repository: custom-repo/agentcube-router\n          tag: v2.0.0\n    asserts:\n      - equal:\n          path: spec.replicas\n          value: 3\n      - equal:\n          path: spec.template.spec.containers[0].image\n          value: custom-repo/agentcube-router:v2.0.0\n\n  - it: should render with extraEnv\n    set:\n      router:\n        extraEnv:\n          - name: CUSTOM_ROUTER_ENV\n            value: router-value\n    asserts:\n      - contains:\n          path: spec.template.spec.containers[0].env\n          content:\n            name: CUSTOM_ROUTER_ENV\n            value: router-value\n\n  - it: should have correct health probes\n    asserts:\n      - equal:\n          path: spec.template.spec.containers[0].livenessProbe.httpGet.path\n          value: /health/live\n      - equal:\n          path: spec.template.spec.containers[0].livenessProbe.httpGet.port\n          value: 8080\n      - equal:\n          path: spec.template.spec.containers[0].livenessProbe.initialDelaySeconds\n          value: 1\n      - equal:\n          path: spec.template.spec.containers[0].livenessProbe.periodSeconds\n          value: 2\n      - equal:\n          path: spec.template.spec.containers[0].readinessProbe.httpGet.path\n          value: /health/ready\n      - equal:\n          path: spec.template.spec.containers[0].readinessProbe.httpGet.port\n          value: 8080\n      - equal:\n          path: spec.template.spec.containers[0].readinessProbe.initialDelaySeconds\n          value: 1\n      - equal:\n          path: spec.template.spec.containers[0].readinessProbe.periodSeconds\n          value: 2\n\n  - it: should render with custom service type and port\n    set:\n      router:\n        service:\n          type: NodePort\n          port: 80\n          targetPort: 8080\n    asserts:\n      - equal:\n          path: spec.type\n          value: NodePort\n        documentIndex: 1\n      - equal:\n          path: spec.ports[0].port\n          value: 80\n        documentIndex: 1\n      - equal:\n          path: spec.ports[0].targetPort\n          value: 8080\n        documentIndex: 1\n","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/manifests/charts/base/tests/agentcube-router_test.yaml"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.\n\nLSP errors detected in other files:\n<diagnostics file=\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/manifests/charts/base/templates/workloadmanager.yaml\">\nERROR [16:9] Block collections are not allowed within flow collections\nERROR [16:11] Missing , or : between flow map items\nERROR [17:1] All mapping items must start at the same column\nERROR [18:11] Block collections are not allowed within flow collections\nERROR [18:13] Missing , or : between flow map items\nERROR [19:1] All mapping items must start at the same column\nERROR [19:7] Implicit keys need to be on a single line\nERROR [19:9] Block collections are not allowed within flow collections\nERROR [19:11] Missing , or : between flow map items\nERROR [19:7] Implicit map keys need to be followed by map values\n</diagnostics>\n\nLSP errors detected in other files:\n<diagnostics file=\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/manifests/charts/base/templates/agentcube-router.yaml\">\n