{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775879481513,"sessionID":"ses_2855a9203ffebYGUS0ExwEQGNY","part":{"id":"prt_d7aaa25bf001k3y1wnjUfw6v57","messageID":"msg_d7aa9bfda001yRjPyogJxeYSaF","sessionID":"ses_2855a9203ffebYGUS0ExwEQGNY","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_4c0521223b81438684ff9de3","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"suite: Volcano Scheduler Tests\ntemplates:\n  - volcano-agent-scheduler-development.yaml\ntests:\n  - it: should not render Volcano scheduler resources when disabled\n    set:\n      volcano:\n        scheduler:\n          enabled: false\n    asserts:\n      - hasDocuments:\n          count: 0\n\n  - it: should render all Volcano scheduler resources when enabled\n    set:\n      volcano:\n        scheduler:\n          enabled: true\n    asserts:\n      - hasDocuments:\n          count: 6\n      - isKind:\n          of: ServiceAccount\n        documentIndex: 0\n      - isKind:\n          of: ConfigMap\n        documentIndex: 1\n      - isKind:\n          of: ClusterRole\n        documentIndex: 2\n      - isKind:\n          of: ClusterRoleBinding\n        documentIndex: 3\n      - isKind:\n          of: Service\n        documentIndex: 4\n      - isKind:\n          of: Deployment\n        documentIndex: 5\n\n  - it: should render with default replicas\n    set:\n      volcano:\n        scheduler:\n          enabled: true\n    asserts:\n      - equal:\n          path: spec.replicas\n          value: 1\n        documentIndex: 5\n\n  - it: should render with custom replicas\n    set:\n      volcano:\n        scheduler:\n          enabled: true\n          replicas: 3\n    asserts:\n      - equal:\n          path: spec.replicas\n          value: 3\n        documentIndex: 5\n\n  - it: should render with custom image\n    set:\n      volcano:\n        scheduler:\n          enabled: true\n          image:\n            repository: custom/vc-agent-scheduler\n            tag: v1.0.0\n    asserts:\n      - equal:\n          path: spec.template.spec.containers[0].image\n          value: custom/vc-agent-scheduler:v1.0.0\n        documentIndex: 5\n\n  - it: should have correct ConfigMap data\n    set:\n      volcano:\n        scheduler:\n          enabled: true\n    asserts:\n      - equal:\n          path: metadata.name\n          value: volcano-agent-scheduler-configmap\n        documentIndex: 1\n      - isNotNull:\n          path: data.agent-scheduler.conf\n        documentIndex: 1\n\n  - it: should have prometheus annotations on service\n    set:\n      volcano:\n        scheduler:\n          enabled: true\n    asserts:\n      - equal:\n          path: metadata.annotations.prometheus\\.io/scrape\n          value: \"true\"\n        documentIndex: 4\n      - equal:\n          path: metadata.annotations.prometheus\\.io/port\n          value: \"8080\"\n        documentIndex: 4\n      - equal:\n          path: spec.ports[0].port\n          value: 8080\n        documentIndex: 4\n\n  - it: should have correct ClusterRoleBinding subject\n    set:\n      volcano:\n        scheduler:\n          enabled: true\n    asserts:\n      - equal:\n          path: roleRef.kind\n          value: ClusterRole\n        documentIndex: 3\n      - equal:\n          path: roleRef.name\n          value: volcano-agent-scheduler\n        documentIndex: 3\n      - equal:\n          path: subjects[0].kind\n          value: ServiceAccount\n        documentIndex: 3\n      - equal:\n          path: subjects[0].name\n          value: volcano-agent-scheduler\n        documentIndex: 3\n\n  - it: should mount config volume and tmp volume\n    set:\n      volcano:\n        scheduler:\n          enabled: true\n    asserts:\n      - equal:\n          path: spec.template.spec.volumes[0].name\n          value: config-volume\n        documentIndex: 5\n      - equal:\n          path: spec.template.spec.volumes[0].configMap.name\n          value: volcano-agent-scheduler-configmap\n        documentIndex: 5\n      - equal:\n          path: spec.template.spec.volumes[1].name\n          value: tmp-volume\n        documentIndex: 5\n      - isNotNull:\n          path: spec.template.spec.volumes[1].emptyDir\n        documentIndex: 5\n","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/manifests/charts/base/tests/volcano-scheduler_test.yaml"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.\n\nLSP errors detected in other files:\n<diagnostics file=\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/manifests/charts/base/templates/workloadmanager.yaml\">\nERROR [16:9] Block collections are not allowed within flow collections\nERROR [16:11] Missing , or : between flow map items\nERROR [17:1] All mapping items must start at the same column\nERROR [18:11] Block collections are not allowed within flow collections\nERROR [18:13] Missing , or : between flow map items\nERROR [19:1] All mapping items must start at the same column\nERROR [19:7] Implicit keys need to be on a single line\nERROR [19:9] Block collections are not allowed within flow collections\nERROR [19:11] Missing , or : between flow map items\nERROR [19:7] Implicit map keys need to be followed by map values\n</diagnostics>\n\nLSP errors detected in other files:\n<diagnostics file=\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/manifests/charts/base/templates/agentcube-router.yaml\">\nERROR [16:9] Block collections are not allowed within flow collections\nERROR [16:11] Missing , or : between flow map items\nERROR [17:1] All mapping items must start at the same column\nERROR [18:11] Block collections are not allowed within flow collections\nERROR [18:13] Missing , or : between flow map items\nERROR [19:1] All mapping items must start at the same column\nERROR [19:7] Implicit keys need to be on a single line\nERROR [19:9] Block collections are not allowed within flow collections\nERROR [19:11] Missing , or : between 