{"type":"text","timestamp":1775879549368,"sessionID":"ses_2855a9203ffebYGUS0ExwEQGNY","part":{"id":"prt_d7aab53760019N1uYkeqJ95ygx","messageID":"msg_d7aab49d2001XGxgVqIULy9Xe1","sessionID":"ses_2855a9203ffebYGUS0ExwEQGNY","type":"text","text":"The Helm Chart for agentcube (AR-030) has been fully implemented. Here's a summary:\n\n## Created Files\n\n### Chart Metadata\n- `Chart.yaml` - Chart metadata (apiVersion v1, version 0.1.0)\n- `values.yaml` - Complete values tree with redis, router, workloadmanager, volcano configuration\n\n### Templates\n- `templates/workloadmanager.yaml` - Workload Manager Deployment + Service with health probes, Redis env vars\n- `templates/agentcube-router.yaml` - Router Deployment + Service with WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL, health probes\n- `templates/rbac/workloadmanager.yaml` - ServiceAccount, ClusterRole, ClusterRoleBinding with full RBAC rules\n- `templates/rbac-router.yaml` - Conditional (router.rbac.create) Role + RoleBinding for secrets access\n- `templates/volcano-agent-scheduler-development.yaml` - Conditional Volcano scheduler (ServiceAccount, ConfigMap, ClusterRole, ClusterRoleBinding, Service, Deployment)\n\n### CRDs\n- `crds/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh_agentruntimes.yaml` - AgentRuntime CRD with podTemplate, targetPort, sessionTimeout\n- `crds/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh_codeinterpreters.yaml` - CodeInterpreter CRD with authMode, template, warmPoolSize\n\n### Unit Tests (helm-unittest)\n- `tests/workloadmanager_test.yaml` - 8 tests for Workload Manager\n- `tests/agentcube-router_test.yaml` - 8 tests for Router\n- `tests/rbac-router_test.yaml` - 6 tests for conditional Router RBAC\n- `tests/volcano-scheduler_test.yaml` - 9 tests for Volcano scheduler\n- `tests/workloadmanager-rbac_test.yaml` - 8 tests for Workload Manager RBAC\n\n## Verification\n- `helm lint` passed with no failures\n- `helm template` renders 10 resources (default) or 16 resources (with Volcano + router RBAC enabled)\n- All conditional templates work correctly","t